<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<body style="margin:0;padding:24px;background:#f4f7ef;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#213117;">
    <div style="max-width:680px;margin:0 auto;">
        <div style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:16px;">
            {% if logo_cid %}
                <img src="{{ logo_cid }}" alt="AgriCloud" style="width:220px;max-width:100%;height:auto;border:0;display:inline-block;">
            {% else %}
                <div style="display:inline-block;padding:12px 18px;border-radius:999px;background:#eef6df;color:#213117;font-size:28px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.4px;">
                    AgriCloud
                </div>
            {% endif %}
        </div>

        <div style="background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #e1ead2;border-radius:24px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 18px 40px rgba(33,49,23,0.08);">
            <div style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#77b81e 0%,#5c9118 100%);padding:28px 32px;color:#ffffff;">
                <div style="display:inline-block;padding:6px 12px;border-radius:999px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.16);font-size:12px;letter-spacing:0.6px;text-transform:uppercase;">
                    Order Update
                </div>
                <h1 style="margin:14px 0 8px;font-size:30px;line-height:1.15;">Your order is confirmed</h1>
                <p style="margin:0;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;opacity:0.95;">
                    We have received your order and started preparing it with care.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div style="padding:32px;">
                <p style="margin:0 0 16px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.7;">Hello {{ order.customer.name }},</p>
                <p style="margin:0 0 20px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.8;color:#425534;">
                    Thank you for shopping with AgriCloud. Your order <strong>#{{ order.id }}</strong> has been confirmed,
                    and we attached a PDF summary so you can keep all the details in one place.
                </p>

                <div style="background:#f8fbf2;border:1px solid #dce8c8;border-radius:20px;padding:22px;margin:24px 0;">
                    <table role="presentation" style="width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;">
                        <tr>
                            <td style="padding:0 0 12px;font-size:14px;color:#6a7d59;">Product</td>
                            <td style="padding:0 0 12px;font-size:16px;font-weight:700;color:#213117;text-align:right;">{{ order.product.name }}</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td style="padding:12px 0;font-size:14px;color:#6a7d59;border-top:1px solid #e2ecd5;">Quantity</td>
                            <td style="padding:12px 0;font-size:16px;font-weight:700;color:#213117;text-align:right;border-top:1px solid #e2ecd5;">{{ order.quantity }} {{ order.product.unit }}</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td style="padding:12px 0;font-size:14px;color:#6a7d59;border-top:1px solid #e2ecd5;">Total</td>
                            <td style="padding:12px 0;font-size:18px;font-weight:700;color:#0f8a47;text-align:right;border-top:1px solid #e2ecd5;">{{ order.totalPrice }} TND</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td style="padding:12px 0 0;font-size:14px;color:#6a7d59;border-top:1px solid #e2ecd5;vertical-align:top;">Delivery</td>
                            <td style="padding:12px 0 0;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;color:#213117;text-align:right;border-top:1px solid #e2ecd5;">
                                {{ order.shippingAddress }}<br>
                                {{ order.shippingCity }}{% if order.shippingPostal %}, {{ order.shippingPostal }}{% endif %}
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                    </table>
                </div>

                <div style="background:#fff8e8;border:1px solid #f1d68d;border-radius:18px;padding:18px 20px;margin:24px 0;">
                    <div style="font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:#8a6400;margin-bottom:6px;">What happens next</div>
                    <div style="font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;color:#6d5820;">
                        You will be able to follow the order status from your account as it moves from confirmation to preparation, shipment, and delivery.
                    </div>
                </div>

                <p style="margin:0;font-size:14px;line-height:1.8;color:#55674a;">
                    We’re happy to have you with us and we’ll keep you updated as your order moves forward.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div style="padding:20px 32px;background:#f8fbf2;border-top:1px solid #e1ead2;font-size:12px;line-height:1.7;color:#738564;text-align:center;">
                Fresh products, clear follow-up, and a simpler marketplace experience with AgriCloud.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
